nodes.text: Dark Valor was a High Commander serving in the Imperial Military. In 1 ABY Dark Valor was spotted in the Dathomir system, piloting a VT-49 Decimator.
Dark Valor appeared in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
